channel.title: You know you play to much rs when
channel.description:
It's not a forum game, just more of something to think about?
I think there was a topic like this awhile back but this is what it goes like..
so.. You know you play to much Rune scape when.. and put a answer? If a moderator wishes to lock it, go ahead.
[b]1[/b]. You know you play to much Rune scape when you get in a fight and say "Oh my god that kid just hit a 50 on me!" [b]2[/b]. You know you play to much Rune scape when your having Sexual relations with your Girlfriend/Boyfriend and say "Yes yes YES!! this is just like killing the kq and getting a dragon chain! [b]3[/b]. when you throw ice cubes at people and scream 'ice barrage'! [b]4[/b]. you set a cape on fire and scream fire cape [b]5[/b]. when someone is thinking you scream "damnit lag!" [b]6[/b]. when someone gives something cant do you say "lemme get on my main" [b]7[/b]. you say w00t when something good happens to you [b]8[/b]. when beat someone up you say " see you in lumby noob" [b]9[/b]. you hate cabbage [b]10[/b]. you dont drink water [b]11[/b]. you never shit [b]12[/b]. you cut down random trees [b]13[/b]. you kill a man [b]14[/b]. when you get a F on a test you say the teacher hacked [b]15[/b]. you havent played a sport for the past year [b]16[/b]. you dont believe in chuck norris, only zezima [b]17[/b]. when someone asks for a dollar you call them a noob and give them 3k and a axe [b]18.[/b]You dress up as a RuneScape NPC for Halloween and run around "stabbing" people or "whipping" them. [b]19.[/b] You pickpocket someone, they catch you and call the police and you say "amg hax he didnt punch me" [b]20.[/b] You know you play too much rs when you call your friends noobs to their face. [b]21.[/b] you know you play to much rune scape when you say "rofl lmao" at a joke. [b]22.[/b] you know you play to much rune scape when you say "were is your sword" to your friend when your fighting. [b]23.[/b] you know you play to much rune scape when you say "I'll fight you in the dual arena" to a bully [b]24.[/b] you know you play to much rune scape when you "fight a person that has a gun, and you have a cardboard cut out of a bow." [b]25.[/b] you know you play to much rune scape "when you make a private server for it, just for the items and to say your awesome." [b]26.[/b] When you take objects that look like knives and say "DDS Spec" and slash at your friends. [b]27.[/b] you know you play to much rune scape "when you cut out a sword and shield and fight your dog and saying AMG I AM BEATING A HELL HOUND!!" [b]28.[/b] You know you play to much rune scape "when you go to the store and yell buying rare items!" [b]29.[/b] you know you play to much rune scape "when you look up rune scape porn" [b]30.[/b] You know you play too much runescape when you make jokes about playing to much runescape. [b]31.[/b] when there are fire works, you say: ' gratz you leveled up!'
Make your own, and I will keep adding them up here.. Try not to make more than 2. You may post reply's to other peoples that they say as long as you have posted 1 or 2. If not then don't bother wasting your time on hitting Reply or Quick Reply.
Any more flaming or spaming the topic, will proceed in a report.

item.description:
@justinxg27 wrote:

Read this, you will then understand it’s internet slang.

en.wikipedia.org

Teh

Teh is an Internet slang neologism most frequently used as an English article, based on a common typographical error of "the". Teh has subsequently developed grammatical usages distinct from the. It is not common in spoken or written English outside technical or leetspeak circles, but when spoken, it is pronounced /tɛ/ or /tə/. Teh originates from the common typo of the, it has become conventionalized in a variety of contexts. As slang, grammatical usage of the word teh is somewhat fluid. Besid...
